text: Rami Hamdallah (; born 10 August 1958) is a Palestinian politician and academic. He was the Prime Minister of the Palestinian National Authority. He also was president of An-Najah National University in Nablus. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of the State of Palestine Category:Prime Ministers of the Palestinian National Authority
title: Rami Hamdallah
